---how to use it

$ docker run --rm \
       -v /path_to_openwrt_git_root_dir:/openwrt \
       -v /path_to_download_dir:/dl \
       njhsi/openwrt_buildroot \
       make menuconfig             # <<<-- direct operation to command here


volumes to give:
and operations: make -j2 -k,  make package/xxx/compile

tag the changes of sources/configs by taging the container into images
  - be minimal: take away build_dir and staging_dir